DECL
# Structure of DECL FULL_NAME DEFAULT_VALUE {SHORT_NAME}
DESCRIP

MeasureCompilation false measureCompilation
Time all compilations and report on exit

stackTraceVMSysWrite false 
Exclusively use VM.sysWrite to print stack dumps

stackTraceAtExit false 
Dump a stack trace (via VM.syswrite) upon exit

stackTraceAlsoToVMSysWrite false
When printing a stack dump, print a copy via VM.sysWrite (if not doing so already)

stackTraceAnnounceWhenPrinting false
Announce via VM.syswrite() when we print a stack trace

stackTraceShowPrintingContext false
Print the context of every attempt to print out a stack trace, to debug problems with the stack trace printing code itself.

TraceClassLoading false verboseTraceClassLoading
More detailed tracing then -verbose:class

ErrorsFatal false errorsFatal
Exit when non-fatal errors are detected; used for regression testing

